<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>EC-16 CONTROLLER - TROUBLESHOOTING - TESTING THE MODULATOR, PART B</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0403224" svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TESTING THE MODULATOR, PART B</title>
        <table id="hl0403226">
            <title>Testing The Modulator, Part B</title>
            <tgroup cols="5">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.77in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="0.82in"/>
                <colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.89in"/>
                <colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.40in"/>
                <colspec colname="5" colwidth="1.45in"/>
                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="5" spanname="s1t5"/>
                <thead>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES-IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Go to modulator and inspect wiring connector. Disconnect connector and test resistance
                                between pins on modulator (
                                <hotlnk xrefid="hl0403227">Resistance Test Table</hotlnk>). Test each pin to vehicle
                                ground and note no continuity. Resistance readings correct?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Replace the modulator.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Off/On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Reconnect connector to modulator. Turn ignition ON and pass magnet over RESET on
                                EC-16. Note reaction of red LEDs. Are any red LEDs illuminated?
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Repeat
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403208.xml" xrefid="hl0403208">INITIAL START-UP
                                    PROCEDURE</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Same red LEDs illuminated?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Repair or replace modulator wire harness.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04032_HL0403214.xml" xrefid="hl0403214">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED
                                    LEDS, PART III</hotlnk>, and retest.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
        <table id="hl0403227">
            <title>Resistance Test</title>
            <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colname="1" colwidth="2.62in"/>
                <colspec colname="2" colwidth="2.58in"/>
                <thead>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">Description</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">Resistance</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>Hold to Common</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Read 3.5 to 5 ohms</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>Exhaust to Common</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Read 3.5 to 5 ohms</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="0">
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>Exhaust to Hold</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Read 7 to 10 ohms</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
